description:
NetOptimizer uses advanced techniques to speed up and optimize Internet connection on your PC. With NetOptimizer you’ll be able to optimize your Internet settings allowing you to recognize your highest Internet speed.

NetOptimizer uses advanced techniques to speed up and optimize Internet connection on your PC. With NetOptimizer you’ll be able to optimize your Internet settings allowing you to recognize your highest Internet speed. Whether you’re connected with a cable, Wi-Fi, or mobile broadband, NetOptimizer will help!

Incorrect Windows settings can slow down your browsing. NetOptimizer will fix all the wrong configurations and make your Internet fly.
Different browsers behave differently. NetOptimizer will automatically apply the optimal settings for all your browsers.
Internet junk can result in slow Internet browsing experience and clog your computer. NetOptimizer will find and clean up the trash for ultimate speed.
